# Audr suppression file for self-scan in CI.
#
# Format:
#   <rule-id>                  disable a rule globally
#   <path-glob>                suppress ALL rules under that path
#   <rule-id> <path-glob>      disable a rule under that path

# testdata/ is fixture-by-design — every file there exists to exercise a
# rule. Suppressing the entire tree is intentional. Real captured tokens
# never live here per AGENTS.md; placeholders only.
testdata/**
